The response before was not super different but from what I remember it was correct: S3, Azure Blob, GCP, Google Drive. Then some info about Instabase drive.

The response isn't wildly wrong, but I think its a nuanced answer that it isn't getting all the details correct on

Agree Hamish! These are the challenges in the retrieval and ranking. We will debug this and give an update! @vineeth Can you check the “pay date” question here, assuming this is easily reproducible in lower environments? Clearly the ranking is messed up somehow!
I also found some mount/data source that were configured to pull all the drives again - so I disabled it. This would likely have led to the ACL issue that  you reported @Hamish
